%% Diagram: LL-HLS — partial segments, blocking playlist reload, preload hints
%% Type: sequence
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Enc as Encoder / Packager
    participant Origin as Origin
    participant CDN as CDN Edge
    participant Player as Player

    Player->>CDN: GET /playlist.m3u8?_HLS_msn=100&_HLS_part=3
    CDN->>Origin: forward (cache miss)
    Note over Origin: hold connection (blocking)
    Enc->>Origin: publish part 3 (~200-1000 ms)
    Origin-->>CDN: 200 + updated playlist (incl. PRELOAD-HINT for part 4)
    CDN-->>Player: playlist + part URIs
    Player->>CDN: GET segment100_part3.m4s
    CDN-->>Player: chunked transfer (parallel with encode)
    Player->>CDN: GET segment100_part4.m4s (preload-hint)
    Note over CDN,Origin: server holds part 4 until ready
    Enc->>Origin: publish part 4
    Origin-->>CDN: chunked bytes
    CDN-->>Player: chunked bytes (~part-target latency)
    Note over Player: Buffer ~1-2 s safety -> total ≈ 2-4 s glass-to-glass
